    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Video subtitle</para>
<para>Any subtitle destined to be displayed by a video output thread should be stored in this structure from it&apos;s creation to it&apos;s effective display. Subtitle type and flags should only be modified by the output thread. Note that an empty subtitle MUST have its flags set to 0. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
